      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/mesh-convergence-gci",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Grid Convergence Index — Three-Level Mesh Refinement Study",
      "description": "Three structured hexahedral meshes (coarse: 1.2M cells, medium: 4.8M cells, fine: 19.2M cells, refinement ratio r=2) were run at the 4 L/min / 3500 RPM nominal operating point. GCI values for predicted RHI were 3.1% (medium) and 0.9% (fine), confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/morrison/activity/mesh-convergence-study-2024q2"
    },
